tagline: This Project Contains Syntax to VBA and VBS for Atom Code editor

### Welcome to Language VBS GitHub Pages.

### Language VBS 
This package is for Atom Code Editor which checks for the Syntax of VB Script which is saved in .VBS format

### Authors and Contributors

This Package is made with Love by Nandan (@NandanSharma)  

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Package? Please feel free to log it in https://github.com/NandanSharma/AtomPackages/issues
